Fiber Optic
	Uses glass fiber to transmit light [[img http://fineartamerica.com/images-medium/fiber-optic-cable-wayne-pascall.jpg]]
	Composed of core, cladding, buffer & Jacket
	Types [[img http://www.l-com.com/lcom_emails/2005/090705/images/fiber_spec.gif]]
		Single-mode
			More difficlt to work with
			Used for long distance runs 
				10-80+ km
		Multi-mode
			Easier to work with
			Used in LANs 
				300-400m
